   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_2_00026"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb34860" type="place">Steindorf</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">am <rs ref="#pmb40374" type="place">Ossiacher See</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine>in <rs ref="#pmb651" type="place">Kärnthen</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_2_00028"/><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1898-07-10">10. 7. 98</date>.</dateline><salute>Lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>morgen Früh rei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e ich ab. Bis Ende der Woche treffen mich Nachrichten im <rs ref="#pmb34018" type="place">Hotel zum Elephanten</rs>in <rs ref="#pmb860" type="place">Graz</rs>. Allerdings nur, we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> man<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ie
                  <pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_2_00029"/>ab<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>endet.</p><p>La<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Sie bald von<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich hören.</p><closer>Von Herzen Ihr <signed>Arthur.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
